name: D/ACC
description: D/ACC is a community driven meme project built on the philosophy of Vitalik Buterin which advocates for a deliberate and balanced path in technological development, comprising; Decentralization, Defensive, Acceleration principles to advance human civilization. With advancement of artificial intelligence, the survival of the human civilization significantly depends on the ability of humanity to establish a balance that ensures safety protocols, limiting or eliminating abuse by tech supremacists.
